      "span_text": "In Figure 3 (b) we validate that our theory not only applies to 1D optimization problems, but also can accurately describe what happens when we run pipeline-parallel SGD on a simple 12-dimensional linear regression problem using the cpusmall dataset  ; the algorithm diverges at precisely an α ∝ τ −1 slope, exactly what Lemma 1 predicts."
